/*
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------
| API Routes (v1)
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Enforcement order:
| 1. auth:sanctum        → authentication
| 2. context.guard      → active operational context
| 3. ability:{domain}.* → token scope ceiling
| 4. Controller authz   → fine-grained permission checks
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------
*/

